snippet.title: Order 13 - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Pack orders and ship them out. But the warehouse holds more than just inventory. Check out the creepy Order 13 teaser trailer for this upcoming single-player horror simulation game. The teaser trailer for Order 13 shows how you can manage and pack orders at a fulfillment center but things quickly turn terrifying while exploring a large warehouse. Order 13 will be available on PC.

#Horror #Gaming #Games
